416
00:17:41,418 --> 00:17:43,817
<i>¿Qué piensas tú, papá?</i>

417
00:17:43,850 --> 00:17:46,217
<i>Pienso que eres raro, Abed.</i>

418
00:17:46,251 --> 00:17:48,351
<i>Y pienso que se acaba de
ir la persona equivocada.</i>

419
00:17:55,583 --> 00:17:57,418
